		<div class="contentstruct">
				<div class="content">
					<h4>How did you start planning your company?</h4>
					<form id="usrform">
					  <p>
						My idea for the company <span onclick="strike(['startOpt2'],['startOpt1'])" id="startOpt1"><u>I'm starting</u></span>/<span onclick="strike(['startOpt1'],['startOpt2'])" id="startOpt2"><u>I've started</u></span> 
